com.telerion.androidsdk

Interface Session


  • public interface Session

    The Session interface represents a signaling and media session between client and telerion service.

    Session can be call or chat. Use SessionType to define what outgoing session to create. Use getSessionType() to read Session type.

    Both chat and call sessions includes caller (originator) and callee (terminator). For outgoing session use setOwnNumber(String) to define caller number and point callee number as parameter of connect(String) method.

    To receive callbacks on session events set listener via setListener(SessionListener) method.
